      "tip": "Taxi & Auto Rickshaw Scams: Driver claims your hotel is 'closed' or 'moved' and takes you to a commission-based shop or hotel- Always negotiate a fare or insist on the meter before boarding a local auto, and insist you are taken to your pre-booked hotel, directly",
